{
  "texts": [
    "For brevity, we refer to CodeLlama-13B-Instruct, CodeLlama-7B-Instruct, DeepSeekCoder-7B-Instruct-V1.5, WizardCoder-15B-V1.0, Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2, CodeQwen1.5-7B-Chat as CodeLlama-13B, CodeLlama-7B, DeepSeekCoder-7B, WizardCoder-15B, Mitral-7B and CodeQWen-7B in the subsequent sections of this paper.",
    "Evaluation Metrics𝑻 𝒐𝒑@𝒌.",
    "To evaluate the performance of the fine-tuned LLMs, we employ the 𝑇𝑜𝑝@𝑘 metric, which assesses the model's ability to generate correct solutions within a limited number of attempts.",
    "The value of 𝑘 represents the number of samples generated for each problem.",
    "In the 𝑇𝑜𝑝@𝑘 evaluation, a problem is considered solved if at least one of the 𝑘 generated samples for that problem passes the corresponding test cases."
  ]
}